# RCbot Help & Support

Welcome to RCbot — here’s how to get help or report issues:

---

## 📚 Documentation

- **Project overview**: RCbot reponds to questions about research computing resources provided by Digital Research Alliance of Canada (formerly Compute Canada) and University of Alberta.

---

## 🛠️ Troubleshooting

- **Didn’t respond?**  
  - Ensure you added RCbot from your Workspace's Marketplace.  
  - Use **“What’s your name?”** to test basic functionality.

- **Formatting issues**? RCbot supports **CardsV2** style tables. Ask in Gmail Chat to test.

- **Chat not working?** Check with your Workspace Administrator whether RCbot is approved for use.

---

## ✍️ Feedback & Bugs

To report issues or request features:

- **Email**: research dot support at ualberta dot ca 
- **Preferred format**:
  1. Short description (e.g., “RCbot is not responding”)
  2. Exact input/output you used
  3. Screenshot of the problem (if available)

---

## 📅 Maintenance & Availability

RCbot runs on Google’s infrastructure and is monitored daily. Planned downtime will be communicated in advance.

---

## 🔐 Data Requests & Privacy

Should you have any concerns or questions, contact us at **research dot support at ualberta dot ca**.
